1
00:00:40,920 --> 00:00:47,008
I really don't want to have to say this, but…

2
00:00:49,890 --> 00:00:52,160
I think it’s best if you keep an eye on my mother.

3
00:00:52,780 --> 00:00:57,080
The thing is... I’ve seen documents in her workroom

4
00:00:57,810 --> 00:01:00,328
that our father actually wrote.

5
00:01:00,736 --> 00:01:06,632
They state that she is supposed to help you manage the company until you turn 25.

6
00:01:07,660 --> 00:01:08,848
If I get the chance,

7
00:01:11,008 --> 00:01:15,192
I’ll try to sneak them out for you to see.

8
00:01:20,090 --> 00:01:21,336
Thank you, Ranya.

9
00:01:23,540 --> 00:01:24,480
You’re welcome.

10
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,632
It’s my duty.

11
00:01:33,450 --> 00:01:36,624
Have they started teaching you the ropes yet?

12
00:01:37,260 --> 00:01:40,760
About the suppliers and buyers?

13
00:01:41,590 --> 00:01:42,984
Would you like to try writing yourself?

14
00:01:43,008 --> 00:01:44,056
I can teach you.

15
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:46,712
I’d love to!

16
00:01:53,110 --> 00:01:54,232
Come closer.

17
00:01:56,840 --> 00:01:57,600
Where do I start?

18
00:01:57,648 --> 00:01:59,776
If you’re going to write these, you need to go into this section here.

19
00:02:02,016 --> 00:02:04,584
Every word we send them has to be 100% accurate.

20
00:02:06,664 --> 00:02:08,400
See what I’m doing here?

21
00:02:11,530 --> 00:02:14,912
Once this part is done, you just type it in like this.

22
00:02:18,370 --> 00:02:21,120
That’s it,it’s actually quite simple.

23
00:03:24,050 --> 00:03:25,816
I’ll leave now.

24
00:06:23,248 --> 00:06:26,016
Oh, and regarding the clients we dealt with this month

25
00:06:26,056 --> 00:06:29,080
The feedback has been excellent.

26
00:06:29,112 --> 00:06:33,424
In fact, it’s the highest percentage we’ve ever achieved.

27
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,800
I want to thank everyone so much.

28
00:06:46,344 --> 00:06:47,888
Thank you so much.

29
00:06:48,390 --> 00:06:53,936
This wouldn’t have turned out so well without Mom and P’Chat’s guidance.

30
00:06:55,420 --> 00:06:58,792
Thank you both very much.

31
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:21,792
Don’t you think the way Mr. Wichai’s two daughters look at each other a bit... strange?

32
00:07:22,810 --> 00:07:23,944
I think so.

33
00:07:50,020 --> 00:07:51,048
Everyone,

34
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:56,608
do you agree with me?

35
00:07:57,290 --> 00:07:59,952
The behavior in the meeting room just now,

36
00:08:00,760 --> 00:08:03,168
those were not the looks that sisters give one another.

37
00:08:29,060 --> 00:08:30,344
Hello, Khun Chat.

38
00:08:30,400 --> 00:08:32,340
I have new evidence I’d like you to see.

39
00:08:50,120 --> 00:08:51,592
What is that mean?

40
00:08:58,432 --> 00:09:00,430
Here. These are the DNA test results.

41
00:09:00,456 --> 00:09:02,560
I’ve had them since Ranya was a child.

42
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:12,816
The DNA results for K’Wichai and K’Ranya do not match.

43
00:09:13,380 --> 00:09:15,432
The results K’Jintana has are fake.

44
00:09:41,490 --> 00:09:42,512
Also, there’s one more matter.

45
00:09:42,536 --> 00:09:44,176
The circumstances of Mr. Wichai’s death.

46
00:09:44,248 --> 00:09:46,008
Would you like me to look into that as well, K’Chat?

47
00:09:58,848 --> 00:09:59,600
Yes, please.
